title: Iyanla Fix My Life Season 4
description:
Iyanla Fix My Life S04E00 Healing In Ferguson WS DSR x264-NY2
In a special report, Iyanla Vanzant embeds herself in the local community and works to empower citizens by helping them formulate a plan for peace and healing in the wake of the shooting death of Michael Brown. Learn more, then tune in Tuesday.

Iyanla.Fix.My.Life.S04E01.Father.With.34.Children.Part.One.
Iyanla comes to the help of a 44-year-old man who is father to 34 children to 17 different women, as well as adopting 9 other children.

Iyanla.Fix.My.Life.S04E02.Father.With.34.Children.Part.Two
Iyanla continues trying to help Jay, as she realizes his issues are to do with his parents.

Iyanla Fix My Life S04E03 Father With 34 Children.Part.Three
Iyanla continues in hoping to help fix out a father of 34 children.

Iyanla Fix My Life S04E04 Follow Up Special WS DSR x264-NY2
During this Iyanla: Fix My Life special event, Iyanla tackles the issue of wounded women settling for wounded men. She's joined in studio by a group of women, including many of the mothers featured on "Fix My Father with 34 Children."

Iyanla.Fix.My.Life.S04E05E06.WS.DSR.x264-[NY2]
Episode 5
In Conyers, Georgia, a family struggles with three generations of woman-on-woman violence.
Episode 6
Jay makes his return to the show.

Iyanla Fix My Life S04E07 The Season Finale WS DSR x264-NY2
Men, women and children help Iyanla to close the conversation on fatherhood.
